title: Spider-Force #2
body:
That was a decent issue. I didn’t really care to much for the Spidernaught. I mean, he looked cool. But his struggle with helping our heroes wasn’t compelling for me. What I did care about were all the astronauts getting eaten. The last people of a dead world getting killed without care. That’s rough. I also liked the flashback bit, though I wish it would have been a little more clear who’s head we were looking into at the time. Really, seeing more of Ashley’s backstory would be cool!

-Chuck
